OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FTrain maker Alstom puts    
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F1,300 jobs at risk         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, More than 1,300 jobs have been put at  
OL,6, risk at the UK's biggest rail assembly 
OL,7, factory.                               
OL,9,FAlstom is consulting on job losses at  
OL,10,Fits Litchurch Lane factory in Derby,   
OL,11,Fwhich has no confirmed workload beyond 
OL,12,Fthe first quarter of 2024.             
OL,14,FWork on trains for HS2 is scheduled to 
OL,15,Fstart at the site in late 2026 but     
OL,16,Fthere is a gap in orders from early    
OL,17,Fnext year.                             
OL,19,FThe BBC understands 550 permanent jobs 
OL,20,Fand 780 temporary jobs are at risk.    
